  <brief_title>A Survey to Evaluate Diabetes Management, Control, Complications and Psychosocial Aspects of Diabetic Patients in Philippines</brief_title>
  <acronym>DiabCare Asia</acronym>
  <official_title>DiabCare Asia 2008 Philippines A Cross-Sectional Survey to Evaluate Diabetes Management, Control, Complications, Psychosocial Aspects of Diabetic Patients in Philippines &amp; To Evaluate Perceptions and Practices of Physicians &amp; Patients About Diabetes Management in Philippines</official_title>
